========================
Installation
========================
Requires BSD-3-Clause licensed JWT class available at:
  https://github.com/firebase/php-jwt

Installation steps:

1. Download and extract the PHP JWT package from https://github.com/firebase/php-jwt into this module's root. JWT.php is required by the module.

Example:
composer require firebase/php-jw
cd <module root>
cp JWT.php .

Adjust require line in the module to match file path if necessary.

2. Access admin/config/people/orcaauth as Drupal administrator user. Enter Base64 encoded Orca JWT secret key. Select "Save Configuration".
